Wild Speed

Using this spell, the druid may borrow for a short
time the speed of such creatures as the hare,
hawk, and cheetah.  He may also confer this
speed on another person.

Command: speed <target> (defaults to caster)
Base Cost: 50 SP
Base Recovery: medium-long
Base Effect: boost (dexterity, moderate)
Base Duration: medium-long
Guild Level: 4
